OL,6,FA woman who killed her abusive partner
OL,7,Fhas been found guilty of murder.
OL,9,F33 year-old Julie Ann McIlwaine, of
OL,10,FKilwee Lane in Dunmurray, stabbed her
OL,11,Fpartner James Crossley to death with a
OL,12,Fkitchen knife.
OL,14,FMcIlwaine had admitted causing the
OL,15,Fdeath of Mr Crossley but denied his
OL,16,Fmurder.
OL,18,FThe 38 year-old victim was killed
OL,19,Fwhile he slept in March 2022.
