OL,6,FAfter deliberating for nearly 10 hours
OL,7,Fat Coleraine Crown Court, a jury of
OL,8,Fseven women and five men reached a
OL,9,Funanimously guilty verdict.
OL,11,FDuring her police interviews McIlwaine
OL,12,Ftold detectives she and Crossley had
OL,13,Fbeen arguing off and on that day but
OL,14,Fas her victim lay sleeping "I was
OL,15,Fgetting all these thoughts in my
OL,16,Fhead...I didn't know what was going
OL,17,Fon...I felt like a psychopath."
