OL,6,F"I didn't want me and him to be
OL,7,Ftogether. I didn't want to happen what
OL,8,Fhappened," the 33-year-old told police
OL,9,Fwho suggested to her "something came
OL,10,Fover you?"
OL,12,F"I couldn't stop, I just kept pushing
OL,13,Fit and pushing it. He said 'Julie Ann
OL,14,Fhelp me'...I took the baby and ran
OL,15,Fout," she told the detectives.
