OL,4,Cabusive partner
OL,6,FShe told police how they first began
OL,7,Ftheir relationship in January 2020 but
OL,8,Fthat between then and the fatal
OL,9,Fstabbing around 23.30 on 1 March 2022,
OL,10,Fthere had been periods of separation
OL,11,Fwith incidents of domestic violence,
OL,12,Fcoercive control and verbal abuse
OL,13,Finterspersed in the relationship which
OL,14,FMcIlwaine was hiding and keeping
OL,15,Fsecret from her friends, family and
OL,16,FSocial Services.
