OL,6,FFollowing the jury's verdict, Mr
OL,7,FJustice Kinney emphasised their role
OL,8,Fwas an "integral part" of the justice
OL,9,Fsystem and thanking them for their
OL,10,Fpatience and the "conscientious way"
OL,11,Fthey had approached the case, he said
OL,12,Fthey had to deal with "very difficult
OL,13,Fevidence."
OL,15,FRemanding McIlwaine into custody, he
OL,16,Fadjourned the case until 6 November.
